&kp C_MUTE        &kp LEFT_GUI  &kp LEFT_ALT  &mo 3   &lt 1 SPACE  &lt 2 SPACE    &to 0            &lt 2 SPACE  &lt 1 SPACE  &mo 3      &kp RIGHT_ALT  &kp RIGHT_GUI
